# Berggruen Prize 2026 rigor history placeholder

Empty by design. The Berggruen Prize submission is **AI-free**
(any AI assistance voids eligibility per prize rules), so the
five-pass rigor cascade + Stage 4 + Stage 5 sign-off pipeline
that applies to all other per-essay packages does NOT apply here.

If author chooses to add offline-generated review notes / draft
audits / version snapshots to this subdirectory, those would be
the only artifacts that ever land here.

This file exists only so the empty `rigor/` directory is tracked
by git (per the per-essay directory layout established 2026-05-28).
